English: You have been rewarded with {0} Booster(s) in exchange for your collected artifacts
Description: A test that informs the player that the artifacts they collected during the last expedition/mission have been traded in for one or more boosters. The way the text combines the singular and plural version of "booster" with a parentheses around the "s" is intentional, to make Warden come across as rigid and machine-like. The "{0}" represents the number of boosters - do not alter that piece of code, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.
